I want to tell you something before you start to download this torrent.
I downloaded the torrent and at this moment I seed it (upload for those who are download now).
I have high speed Internet connection and it was 4 days for me while I downloaded the full torrent...
I see that many of you only want to download everything and don't want to upload nothing. These members are download slower the torrent than those who download (seed) and upolad (leech) at the same time. If you don't upload the files for the others, you will finish it 1 or 2 days later.
Setup your Torrent application to high priority and please be PATIENT!
And some more information: the last 10% will very hard and very slow because your computer must gather (collect) only those files (slices) which are required to finish the torrent.
